description:
ITV Tour de France 2016 Stage 9 PDTV x264-NX

10th July 2016 ITV4
13:00 to 17:00 Stage 9

Gary Imlach and Chris Boardman present live coverage of stage 9. The stage takes the riders across four major categorised climbs before embarking on the final ascent at the winter sports resort of Andorra Arcalis in the Pyrenees. Officially 10.1km at a gradient of 7.2 per cent, the final mountain pass has a long uphill preamble that makes for a colossal 18km climb. Commentary by Ned Boulting and David Millar with Daniel Friebe reporting from the roadside.
